paragraphs.text:
%livy2.spark

val renameOutpatient_Efficiency = nOutpatient_Efficiency.withColumnRenamed("Facility Name","Facility_Name").withColumnRenamed("Measure ID","Measure_ID").withColumnRenamed("Start Date","Start_Date").withColumnRenamed("End Date","End_Date")

        
val replaceOutpatient_Efficiency = renameOutpatient_Efficiency.withColumn(
    "Score",
    when(
        $"Score".equalTo("Not Available"),
        null
        ).otherwise($"Score")).withColumn(
    "Score",
    when(
        $"Score".equalTo("0.000"),
        "0"
        ).otherwise($"Score")).withColumn(
    "Start_Date",
    when(
        $"Start_Date".equalTo("Not Available"),
        null
        ).otherwise($"Start_Date")).withColumn(
    "End_Date",
    when(
        $"End_Date".equalTo("Not Available"),
        null
        ).otherwise($"End_Date"))

val dropOutpatient_Efficiency = replaceOutpatient_Efficiency.na.drop()
dropOutpatient_Efficiency.show(500)
